      "span_text": "VisTrails  captures the notion of an evolving dataflow, and implements a history management mechanism to maintain versions of a dataflow, thus allowing a scientist to return to previous steps, apply a dataflow instance to different input data, explore the parameter space of the dataflow, and (while performing these steps) compare the associated visualization results."
